{"word":"ἀσπάσιος","slug":"ἀσπάσιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀσπάσιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀσπάζομαι'><el>ἀσπάζομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>welcome, gladly welcomed</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>well-pleased, glad</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:— <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-ίως</el>, <i>gladly</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}